      <title>斯塔默称工党不会考虑征收足球转会税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/labour-not-looking-at-football-transfer-tax-starmer-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 表示，他的政党不打算对英超足球计划中的球员转会征税，这与他的政党的一位高层成员周一表示仍在考虑中的想法相矛盾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/labour-not-looking-at-football-transfer-tax-starmer-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 09:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将为无证公民配偶提供合法身份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/over-500-000-immigrants-to-get-us-legal-status-in-new-biden-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将宣布为 50 多万移民提供获得合法身份的简化途径，这是他的政府迄今为止在提供驱逐出境保护方面做出的最广泛的努力，同时试图反驳一些盟友对他最近的边境镇压行动的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/over-500-000-immigrants-to-get-us-legal-status-in-new-biden-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 试图撤销禁令，考验议员简报的保密性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/tiktok-s-bid-to-overturn-us-ban-tests-secrecy-of-lawmakers-classified-briefings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列仍属机密的简报会后，美国立法者迅速通过了 TikTok 禁令。现在，这款应用的中国所有者正利用这一秘密，以高风险的方式推翻这项新法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/tiktok-s-bid-to-overturn-us-ban-tests-secrecy-of-lawmakers-classified-briefings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国成立专门部门打击俄罗斯虚假信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/germany-launches-unit-to-thwart-alleged-russian-disinformation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国成立了一个专门的工作组来应对柏林政府所称旨在破坏民主和制造社会不和的虚假宣传活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/germany-launches-unit-to-thwart-alleged-russian-disinformation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 08:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥地利部长如何拯救欧盟最令人痛恨的气候法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/how-an-austrian-minister-saved-the-eu-s-most-hated-climate-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自欧盟主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩 (Ursula von der Leyen) 于 2019 年首次提出欧盟绿色协议以来，欧盟已通过了 50 多项法律，但没有一项像重新开发欧洲大陆五分之一陆地和海洋的计划那样引起争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/how-an-austrian-minister-saved-the-eu-s-most-hated-climate-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞的政党要求法国选民获得绝对多数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/le-pen-s-party-says-it-needs-absolute-majority-to-govern-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国民联盟领导人乔丹·巴德拉呼吁支持者帮助他的政党及其盟友在法国的提前选举中取得压倒性胜利，以便他能够执政，为极右翼掌握政策制定权设定了高标准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/le-pen-s-party-says-it-needs-absolute-majority-to-govern-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 06:38:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国议员将与达赖喇嘛会面 中国发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-law-on-tibet-puts-pressure-on-china-for-talks-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国警告美国国会议员本周在达赖喇嘛高调访问期间不要与达赖喇嘛会面，预计他们还将与西藏流亡政府举行会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-law-on-tibet-puts-pressure-on-china-for-talks-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 05:48:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国官员的言论被爆红 为澳大利亚之行蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-s-cheng-lei-gaffe-overshadows-premier-li-qiang-s-australia-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国官员阻拦记者、曾被拘留的成蕾的行为，有可能给李强总理访问澳大利亚带来影响，澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯表示，他对此行为感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-s-cheng-lei-gaffe-overshadows-premier-li-qiang-s-australia-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:19:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非政府合作伙伴准备展开内阁之争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/south-african-elections-new-government-partners-eye-cabinet-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 准备宣誓就职，但由于 5 月 29 日的选举未能产生绝对胜利者，南非各政党上周同意组成执政联盟，并准备在内阁职位上展开争夺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/south-african-elections-new-government-partners-eye-cabinet-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>危机加深 他信、泰国总理陷入法律诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦因侮辱王室一案面临审判，而最高法院命令他的盟友兼总理斯雷塔·塔维辛提交更多证据以要求罢免他，这一举动加剧了这个东南亚国家的政治危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
